333
00:31:40,992 --> 00:31:41,993
Hog Hug.

334
00:31:43,077 --> 00:31:43,870
¡Hogarth Hughes!

335
00:31:48,791 --> 00:31:51,044
Kent Mansley. Del gobierno.

336
00:31:51,085 --> 00:31:53,296
